CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 19, reads: "National, Local Wares Thrill Throng ... 6. Mrs. Esther Austin added extra glamour to the magic beauty of the 1957 Dodge display... - Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Esther Brooks Austin posed next to Dodge car, with banner inscribed "Welcome to the...Wonderful World of Auto Dynamics," at 1957 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Syria Mosque, Oakland
